node.text:
Surrounded by her friends and scenic
landscapes, @dianakunst embarked on a trip to capture and celebrate Mediterranean culture. Beautiful and inspiring, the film shows an ethos that you can take with you and enjoy wherever you are. Born or made, Mediterraneans of the world, this is your home.
See the full short film on our YouTube channel now. 
#MangoTogether

node.title: A MEDITERRANEAN DREAM, an exclusive film by @dianakunst

Surrounded by her friends and scenic
landscapes, @dianakunst embarked on a trip to capture and celebrate Mediterranean culture. Beautiful and inspiring, the film shows an ethos that you can take with you and enjoy wherever you are. Born or made, Mediterraneans of the world, this is your home.
See the full short film on our YouTube channel now. 
#MangoTogether
